---
import Section from './Section.astro';
import Button from './Button.astro';
---

<Section class="my-24 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 reveal" padding="none">
  <div class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
    <!-- Background image with overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?q=80&w=1400&auto=format&fit=crop"
        alt="Jardim vertical fundo"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        width="1400"
        height="600"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/90 via-primary/80 to-[#1b4332]/95"></div>
      <!-- Decorative shapes -->
      <div class="absolute -top-32 -left-32 w-80 h-80 bg-white/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-32 -right-32 w-96 h-96 bg-accent/15 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="relative z-10 text-white text-center py-20 px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 rounded-full px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide mb-8">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent animate-pulse"></span>
        Atendimento via WhatsApp · Sem burocracia
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight font-serif">
        Pronto para Trazer a<br/>Natureza para o Seu Espaço?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/85 mb-10">
        Entre em contato agora pelo WhatsApp e receba um orçamento personalizado, sem compromisso.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
        <Button 
          href="https://wa.me/message/UFIXHURQVOMGD1" 
          style="solid-white-large"
          class="w-full sm:w-auto transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <span class="flex items-center gap-3 justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
            </svg>
            FALAR COM A CARMEN NO WHATSAPP
          </span>
        </Button>
        
        <p class="text-white/75 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 15 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
          </svg>
          Ou venha visitar nosso showroom: Rua Juncal, nº 40 — Jardim Europa, Porto Alegre/RS
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
